eral states in conventional pistol, and a former National Champion, competition shooter with various awards.\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n|bgcolor=\"darkgray\"|{{hs|20}}\n|align=\"center\"| 9th Place\n|-\n| '''Denny Chapman'''<br><small>41, [[Ocala, Florida|Ocala, FL]]</small>\n| [[Cowboy Mounted Shooting]] competitor, horse trainer, Wild West entertainer, former benchrest rifle and USPSA/IPSC three-gun competitor\n| bgcolor=\"red\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Red Team</span>\n|bgcolor=\"darkgray\"|{{hs|20}}\n|align=\"center\"| 8th Place\n|-\n| '''[[Blake Miguez]]'''<br><small>28, [[New Iberia, Louisiana|New Iberia, LA]]</small>\n| Corporate lawyer, semi-professional shooter, [[United States Practical Shooting Association|USPSA]] Grand Master, [[Louisiana]] state champion\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n| bgcolor=\"green\" rowspan=\"7\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Green Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"| 7th Place\n|-\n| '''Adam Benson'''<br><small>44, [[Baltimore, Maryland|Baltimore, MD]]</small>\n| Construction project manager, former [[United States Marine Corps|Marine]], [[United States Practical Shooting Association|USPSA]] Master\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"| 6th Place\n|-\n| '''[[Kelly Bachand]]'''<br><small>22, [[Kent, Washington|Kent, WA]]</small>\n| Student, competition shooter, USA [[National Rifle Team]]\n| bgcolor=\"red\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Red Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"| 5th Place\n|-\n| '''Peter Palma'''<br><small>29, [[Norristown, Pennsylvania|Norristown, PA]]</small>\n| Plumber, [[United States Marine Corps|Marine]] [[Scout Sniper]]\n| bgcolor=\"red\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Red Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"| 4th Place\n|-\n| '''[[J.J. Racaza|Simon \"J.J.\" Racaza]]'''<br><small>29, [[New Milford, New Jersey|New Milford, NJ]]</small>\n| [[United States Department of Homeland Security|Department of Homeland Security]] Agent, double grandmaster in the [[United States Practical Shooting Association|USPSA]]/[[International Practical Shooting Confederation|IPSC]]\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"| 3rd Place\n|-\n| '''Chris Cerino'''<br><small>40, [[Wadsworth, Ohio|Wadsworth, OH]]</small>\n| Law enforcement trainer, 42nd place in the International Law Enforcement Educators and Trainers Association\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"|2nd place\n|-\n| '''[[Iain Harrison]]'''<br><small>42, [[Sherwood, Oregon|Sherwood, OR]]</small>\n| Construction manager, former [[British Army]] platoon commander, [[gunsmith]], competition shooter with various awards\n| bgcolor=\"blue\" align=\"center\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">Blue Team</span>\n|align=\"center\"|Winner\n|}\n\n==Contestant progress==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|#!!rowspan=2|Contestants!!colspan=13|Episodes\n|-\n!1!!2!!3!!4!!5!!6!!7!!8!!colspan=2|9!!colspan=3|10\n|-\n!1\n|bgcolor=\"blue\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">''Iain''</span>\n|bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"pink\"|NOM||bgcolor=\"white\"|SAFE||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"white\"|SAFE||bgcolor=\"white\"|SAFE||bgcolor=\"purple\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">WIN</span>||bgcolor=\"purple\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">WIN</span>||bgcolor=\"limegreen\"|'''TOP SHOT'''\n|-\n!2\n|bgcolor=\"blue\"|<span style=\"color:white;\">''Chris''</span>\n|bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"white\"|SAFE||bgcolor=\"white\"|SAFE||bgcolor=\"cornflowerblue\"|WIN||bgcolor=\"cornflowe